data.text: Local LDS church genealogist Robert Wank, left and history writer David Desmond, right, both residents of Victorville, recently visited Herb Jeffries, 94, a singing cowboy movie star of the late 1930s. They interviewed Jeffries about his life and family history For more information about Jeffries, visit his Web site at www.herbjeffries. com.
